{"tid":1886724,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"如果依家撤樓市辣招會點？","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T03:52:06.000Z","uid":215648,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"07a9487edc9da5e4c66b07422ae5b23a52e845d9","tid":1886724,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"陳帆回應會否撤樓市辣招時稱有需要時會採取適當行動<br />\n19.02.2020 13:38<br />\n運輸及房屋局長陳帆在立法會回應議員質詢時表示，不同時期推出的樓市「辣招」都有背後考量，應對當時的問題，政府會密切留意樓市發展，有需要時會採取適當行動。<br />\n<br />\n地產及建造界石禮謙表示，擔心香港會再出現大量負資產個案，促請政府撤回樓市「辣招」，並要求當局交代「撤辣」的具體日期。陳帆就指，疫情之下，很多事情急速發展，即使政府目前提出具體日期，也不會可信，強調當局會審時度勢。"},{"pid":"d47a41a4749358574d3ec5b2b80c61a3e3d21d16","tid":1886724,"uid":248578,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"睇撤邊樣<br />\n撤BSD 就屌佢老味啦<br />\n撤SSD應該有利增加二手供應"},{"pid":"98c74e36db10e63901f903df70d2780ec0e4a7e5","tid":1886724,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"仲有份工同銀行肯借錢俾你先算啦"},{"pid":"b313068f335f392f08f62a286fb5674fcd9487f7","tid":1886724,"uid":257272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d9f24eabda1f54c4fd831e832fecc50ff9729c4e","tid":1886724,"uid":215648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"撤SSD樓價會唔會大跌？"},{"pid":"fa5b196b83d8fa930a8057d988a0f93d7660a0a9","tid":1886724,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"FREE FALL"},{"pid":"b0e19155243a7b7cd8bead2d47c571611788448c","tid":1886724,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5b196b83d8fa930a8057d988a0f93d7660a0a9","tid":1886724,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"FREE FALL"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"個個都估跌 緊係會升啦<br />\n政府根本就想　keep住升"},{"pid":"aab345cdc434d8c84a85339f053a11449a0503ee","tid":1886724,